 load donor H0351.2001 flat file into DuckDB

- Pivot from broken human_microarray_expression API to bulk flat file download
- Load 58,692 probes across 29,131 genes, 363 samples, 21.3M rows
- DuckDB-side join to avoid Pandas memory ceiling on large melt
- First analytical query confirms BDNF highest in dentate gyrus (left)
- Bug report filed with Allen Institute forum (recurring API outage)
